	<h1 class="title">到了 2018 年，伦敦出租车就将换成零排放的吉利 TX5</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-26 06:10:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16538/medium/16538.jpg?1445589709" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="16538" data-title="《到了 2018 年，伦敦出租车就将换成零排放的吉利 TX5》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16538/medium/16538.jpg?1445589709" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16538.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
